OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777424607
OL,3,CWar propels BP back into 'cash money'
OL,4,Cterritory
OL,6,FThe company is making the really big
OL,7,Fmoney not from selling fuel to drivers
OL,8,F- petrol sales are slightly down on
OL,9,Flast year - but from buying and
OL,10,Fselling oil and gas and refining it.
OL,12,FTraders have cashed in on the wild
OL,13,Fswings in energy prices, and BP's
OL,14,Frefineries have been working flat out,
OL,15,Fturning crude into petrol, diesel, jet
OL,16,Ffuel and marine fuel for ships.
OL,18,FLife looks pretty easy for BP at the
OL,19,Fmoment. But the new chief executive
OL,20,Fsays windfall taxes would be a "highly
OL,21,Fflawed response" to the Iran war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
