OL,3,CWar propels BP back into 'cash money'
OL,4,Cterritory
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMeg O'Neill told the Financial Times
OL,12,Fthe company was working "exceptionally
OL,13,Fhard" to get energy to customers, and
OL,14,Fsaid there was an opportunity to work
OL,15,Fwith governments around the world -
OL,16,Fincluding in Britain, where she
OL,17,Fpointed to "untapped potential" in the
OL,18,FNorth Sea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
