OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777424607
OL,3,CWar propels BP back into 'cash money'
OL,4,Cterritory
OL,6,FOnly about 10% of the group's earnings
OL,7,Fcome from the UK, where BP's North Sea
OL,8,Fbusiness is already subject to a
OL,9,Fwindfall levy - which brings the
OL,10,Feffective tax rate on its profits up
OL,11,Fto 78%.
OL,13,FThere is zero prospect of the UK
OL,14,FTreasury being able siphon a share of
OL,15,Fthe spoils from the Azerbaijan, the US
OL,16,For the many other countries in which
OL,17,FBP operates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
