FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777424607
OL,3,CWar propels BP back into 'cash money'
OL,4,Cterritory
OL,6,FAround one fifth of BP's oil and gas
OL,7,Fproduction comes from the Middle East
OL,8,F- in Oman, Abu Dhabi and Iraq - areas
OL,9,Fnow caught up in the conflict.
OL,11,FBP says it expects disruption will
OL,12,Fcontinue to restrict production in the
OL,13,Fcoming months.
OL,15,FThe group assumes Brent Crude will
OL,16,Faverage $82 a barrel for the full year
OL,17,Fand that "the ongoing supply
OL,18,Fdisruptions as a result of the
OL,19,Fconflict in the Middle East resolve
OL,20,Fbefore the year end 2026".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
